snippet.textDisplay: Relaxing. Dig V and Neha Kakkar bring a fresh vibe, but Kamala Devi truly shines in this song, giving you goosebumps with her performance. Impressive. This exposure not only turned me into a fan but also unveiled the enchanting charm of Uttarakhand's musical legacy, with its soulful tunes and captivating rhythms. Kudos to the Coke Studio Bharat team for delivering such a gem to us. A heartfelt applause to everyone involved in creating this masterpiece
